      "comment": "SILVER SQUEEZE (2) made contact with another runner and could manage only a distant fourth (19.19) in a Maiden over 320m at Richmond. Key player on best form and expected to bounce back. ZIPPER DAY (4) is a handily bred pup making his debut without a trial. Expected to feature on debut. NARROW ARROW (8) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 0.8 lengths second (22.80) behind Regis Krystal at this track. Can feature again. CLYBURN (7) is a newcomer from the Raymond Webster kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Can run a bold race on debut.",
